      <exercise id="fs-id1169738220305" type="problems-exercises">
        <problem id="fs-id1169738247169">  
      <para xmlns:q="http://cnx.rice.edu/qml/1.0" id="import-auto-id1169738077979">Suppose you have an ideal refrigerator that cools an environment at <m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">−</m:mo><m:mtext>20</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>.</m:mtext><m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mtext>º</m:mtext><m:mtext>C</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{-"20" "." 0°C} {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math> and has heat transfer to another environment at <m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mtext>50</m:mtext><m:mtext>.</m:mtext><m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mtext>º</m:mtext><m:mtext>C</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{"50" "." 0°C} {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math>. What is its coefficient of performance?</para></problem></exercise>
      
